name: Zool: Ninja of the 'Nth' Dimension
overview: NINJA BATTLES IN THE "Nth" DIMENSION An interstellar dweller is about to hit your Super NES. He's Zool, the defender of the Nth dimension (your imagination), and a thorn in the side of Krool, his arch enemy. Battle your way through six worlds and a multitude of Krool's armed and dangerous minions. Keep the gateway to your imagination open. Way weird! Way fun!
